Michael C. Lukemire 
Executive Compensation
As President and Chief Operating Officer at SCOTTS MIRACLE-GRO CO, Michael C. Lukemire  made $3,058,862 in total compensation.  Of this total $687,500 was received as a salary, $900,717 was received as a bonus, $579,214 was received in stock options, $800,053 was awarded as stock and $91,378 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


ENTER AN EXECUTIVE OR COMPANY NAME
