Company Profile

Business DescriptionScotts Miracle-Gro Co. engages in the manufacturing, marketing, and sale of consumer branded products for lawn and garden care. It operates through the following segments: U.S. Consumer, Europe Consumer, and Other. The U.S. Consumer segment offers consumer lawn and garden business in the United States. The Europe Consumer segment includes consumer lawn and garden business located in Europe. The Other segment consists of consumer lawn and garden business in the U.S. and Europe. The company was founded by Orlando McLean Scott in 1868 and is headquartered in Marysville, OH. View company web site for more detailsAddress14111 Scottslawn RoadMarysville, Ohio 43041Phone+1.937.644.0011Number of Employees5,100Recent SEC Filing07/05/20174 Chairman & Chief Executive OfficerJames HagedornPresident & Chief Operating OfficerMike LukemireChief Financial Officer & Executive Vice PresidentRandy ColemanSenior VP-Global Technology & OperationsDave Swihart





